    <id>nextcloud_chat</id>
    <name>Nextcloud Chat</name>
    <summary>Matrix-based chat and video calling for Nextcloud using Element</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
        A modern chat and video calling solution for Nextcloud powered by Matrix protocol and Element Web.
        
        Features:
        - Secure end-to-end encrypted messaging
        - High-quality video calls with Element Call
        - Federation with other Matrix homeservers
        - Integration with Nextcloud ecosystem
        - Modern Vue 3 interface
        
        Requires Element Server Suite setup for full functionality.
    ]]></description>
